# CRS Fixer - Harita Hive Professional Tool
# MIT License
#
# Auto-detects & reprojects mismatched CRS in bulk datasets
# Handles thousands of files with intelligent projection detection
#
# Features:
# - Automatic CRS detection using spatial patterns
# - Bulk reprojection with parallel processing
# - Smart projection recommendation based on data extent
# - Handles corrupted or missing .prj files
# - Supports 6000+ coordinate reference systems
# - Batch processing with progress tracking
#
# Supported Formats:
# - All GDAL/OGR supported formats
# - Automatic format detection
# - Preserves original data structure
#
# Usage:
# crs-fixer --input-dir datasets/ --target-crs EPSG:4326 --output-dir fixed/
# crs-fixer --auto-detect file.shp --recommend-crs
# crs-fixer --batch-process *.tif --parallel 8